<item>
            <title>[LU-13627] e2fsprogs 1.45.6 (and older?) build problem on Ubuntu due to ext2_types-wrapper.h</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13627</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Due to commit&#160;3b2ad5cdb4833f052f4ac3d058e5adb8d55ab1ec in master-luster of e2fsprogs the build fails on Ubuntu.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ext2_types-wrapper.h doesn&apos;t belong in&#160;HFILES_IN since it is not generated into the build dir through a .in file. And a corresponding piece of code to make ext2_types.h into ext2_types-%(arch).h etc is missing in debian/rules.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
